text: Imtiaz Anees (born 25 December 1970) is an Indian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Indian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of India Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in equestrian Category:Equestrians at the 1998 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for India Category:Medalists at the 1998 Asian Games
